==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: yóuyú

===Conjunction===
'''[[由]][[于]]'''

# [[because]]; [[since]]
#: '''''由于'''[[他]][[学习]][[三心二意]]，[[期终考试]][[没有]][[通过]]''
#: '''''Because''' he studied half-heartedly, he did not pass the final exam''
#: '''''由于'''[[肚子]][[疼]][[得]][[厉害]]，[[因此]][[才]][[没来]][[上课]]''
#: '''''Since''' I had a bad stomach ache, I did not attend class''

===Preposition===
'''[[由]][[于]]'''

# [[owing to]]; [[due to]]; [[as a result of]]
#: '''''由于'''[[阴天]]，[[没法子]][[晒]][[被子]]''
#: '''''Owing to''' it being overcast, I did not hang out the blankets to dry''
#: ''[[他们]]'''由于'''[[各种]][[原因]]，[[没有]][[去]][[成]]''
#: '''''Owing to''' a number of reasons, they were not able to go''

===Alternate forms===
[[由於]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

